title: This, That Or The Other VIII
teaser: In this installment of an AMA classic, contestants must distinguish between indie bands, Dungeons & Dragons monsters and foreign films. (Not to be confused with foreign bands or indie films.)
contentencoded:
In this installment of an AMA classic, contestants must distinguish between indie bands, Dungeons & Dragons monsters and foreign films. Not to be confused with foreign bands or indie films, of course.
